   <body>
      <p>
         <uicontrol>Agreement Templates</uicontrol> provide an efficient way of setting up the
         default values and settings for your agreements. <uicontrol>Agreement Templates</uicontrol>
         include predefining agreement fields like Agreement Name, Message, Signature Type,
         Language, various Agreement Options, various Agreement Security options, and Mapping
         Options. You can preset the recipient details, file attachments, expiration date, days
         until expiration, reminders as well.</p>
